he was some drunk.

1103
02:15:41,214 --> 02:15:45,913
No, it was a dereliction of my duty.

1104
02:15:51,925 --> 02:15:57,022
If only I'd taken him in,
like I first intended,

1105
02:15:57,764 --> 02:16:00,597
he'd never have ended up...

